(960, 176, 'post_content_2_copy', 'Eat Up is all about changing that. With the generous help and lunch-making skills of a dedicated army of hospitality students and volunteers, we make and deliver thousands of lunches a month to schools in metropolitan Melbourne and regional Victoria. In fact, since 2013, we’ve delivered over 80,000 lunches. Which is over 80,000 afternoons of learning salvaged from the grips of hunger. And we’ll keep going until all of Australia’s hungry school kids are fed.\r\n\r\nEat. Learn. Grow. It’s so simple, a kid would get it.'),
